<h2>oihana-php-arango</h2>
<p>Composable PHP toolkit for <a href="https://www.arangodb.com/" target="_blank">ArangoDB</a>. Part of the <strong>Oihana PHP</strong> ecosystem, this package bundles a modern HTTP client, a high-level façade, document/edge models, controllers, helpers and CLI commands — everything you need to build an ArangoDB-backed application end-to-end.</p>

